{
  "video_id": "NMr3ShT_Kl4",
  "title": "Geoff Mulgan: A short intro to the Studio School",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 18259.0,
      "text": "What I want to talk about today is one idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 20260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an idea for a new kind of school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "which turns on its head much of our conventional thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "about what schools are for and how they work."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 28260.0,
      "text": "And it might just be coming to a neighborhood near you soon."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "Where it comes from"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "is an organization called the Young Foundation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 34260.0,
      "text": "which, over many decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 37260.0,
      "text": "has come up with many innovations in education, like the Open University"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "and things like Extended Schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "Schools for Social Entrepreneurs, Summer Universities"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 44260.0,
      "text": "and the School of Everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "And about five years ago, we asked"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "what was the most important need for innovation"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "in schooling here in the U.K."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "And we felt the most important priority"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 55260.0,
      "text": "was to bring together two sets of problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55260.0,
      "end_time": 57260.0,
      "text": "One was large numbers of bored teenagers"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57260.0,
      "end_time": 59260.0,
      "text": "who just didn&#39;t like school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "couldn&#39;t see any relationship between what they learned in school"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "and future jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 65259.0,
      "text": "And employers who kept complaining"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 65260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68260.0,
      "text": "that the kids coming out of school weren&#39;t actually ready for real work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68260.0,
      "end_time": 70260.0,
      "text": "didn&#39;t have the right attitudes and experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 70260.0,
      "end_time": 72260.0,
      "text": "And so we try to ask:"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 74260.0,
      "text": "What kind of school would have the teenagers fighting to get in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 74260.0,
      "end_time": 77260.0,
      "text": "not fighting to stay out?"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 77260.0,
      "end_time": 79260.0,
      "text": "And after hundreds of conversations"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 79260.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "with teenagers and teachers and parents"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 83260.0,
      "text": "and employers and schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 83260.0,
      "end_time": 85260.0,
      "text": "from Paraguay to Australia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 85260.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "and looking at some of the academic research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 89260.0,
      "text": "which showed the importance"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 89260.0,
      "end_time": 91260.0,
      "text": "of what&#39;s now called non-cognitive skills --"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 91260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "the skills of motivation, resilience --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 96260.0,
      "text": "and that these are as important"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 96260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "as the cognitive skills -- formal academic skills --"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 101260.0,
      "text": "we came up with an answer, a very simple answer in a way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 101260.0,
      "end_time": 103260.0,
      "text": "which we called the Studio School."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 103260.0,
      "end_time": 105260.0,
      "text": "And we called it a studio school"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 105260.0,
      "end_time": 109260.0,
      "text": "to go back to the original idea of a studio in the Renaissance"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 109260.0,
      "end_time": 111260.0,
      "text": "where work and learning are integrated."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 111260.0,
      "end_time": 113260.0,
      "text": "You work by learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 113260.0,
      "end_time": 115260.0,
      "text": "and you learn by working."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 115260.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "And the design we came up with had the following characteristics."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 120260.0,
      "text": "First of all, we wanted small schools --"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 120260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "about 300, 400 pupils --"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "14 to 19 year-olds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 127260.0,
      "text": "and critically, about 80 percent of the curriculum done"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 127260.0,
      "end_time": 129259.0,
      "text": "not through sitting in classrooms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 129258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131260.0,
      "text": "but through real-life, practical projects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 131260.0,
      "end_time": 133260.0,
      "text": "working on commission"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 133260.0,
      "end_time": 135260.0,
      "text": "to businesses, NGO&#39;s and others."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 135260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "That every pupil would have a coach, as well as teachers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "who would have timetables"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 142260.0,
      "text": "much more like a work environment in a business."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 144260.0,
      "text": "And all of this will be done within the public system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 144260.0,
      "end_time": 146260.0,
      "text": "funded by public money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 146260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "but independently run."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 148260.0,
      "end_time": 151260.0,
      "text": "And all at no extra cost, no selection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 151260.0,
      "end_time": 154260.0,
      "text": "and allowing the pupils the route into university,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 157260.0,
      "text": "even if many of them would want to become entrepreneurs"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 157260.0,
      "end_time": 159260.0,
      "text": "and have manual jobs as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 159260.0,
      "end_time": 162260.0,
      "text": "Underlying it was some very simple ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 162260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "that large numbers of teenagers learn best by doing things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 167260.0,
      "text": "they learn best in teams"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 167260.0,
      "end_time": 170260.0,
      "text": "and they learn best by doing things for real --"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 170260.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "all the opposite of what mainstream schooling"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 172260.0,
      "end_time": 174260.0,
      "text": "actually does."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 174260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "Now that was a nice idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 179260.0,
      "text": "so we moved into the rapid prototyping phase."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 179260.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "We tried it out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "first in Luton --"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "famous for its airport and not much else, I fear --"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "and in Blackpool -- famous for its beaches and leisure."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 190260.0,
      "text": "And what we found -- and we got quite a lot of things wrong"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 190260.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "and then improved them --"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "but we found that the young people loved it."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 197260.0,
      "text": "They found it much more motivational, much more exciting"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 197260.0,
      "end_time": 199260.0,
      "text": "than traditional education."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 199260.0,
      "end_time": 201260.0,
      "text": "And perhaps most important of all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 204260.0,
      "text": "two years later when the exam results came through,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 204260.0,
      "end_time": 206260.0,
      "text": "the pupils who had been put on these field trials"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 206260.0,
      "end_time": 208260.0,
      "text": "who were in the lowest performing groups"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 208260.0,
      "end_time": 210260.0,
      "text": "had jumped right to the top --"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 210260.0,
      "end_time": 213260.0,
      "text": "in fact, pretty much at the top decile of performance"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 213260.0,
      "end_time": 215260.0,
      "text": "in terms of GCSE&#39;s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 215260.0,
      "end_time": 218260.0,
      "text": "which is the British marking system."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 218260.0,
      "end_time": 220260.0,
      "text": "Now not surprisingly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 220260.0,
      "end_time": 223260.0,
      "text": "that influenced some people to think we were onto something."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 225260.0,
      "text": "The minister of education"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 225260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "down south in London"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "described himself as a \"big fan.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 232260.0,
      "text": "And the business organizations thought we were onto something"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 232260.0,
      "end_time": 234260.0,
      "text": "in terms of a way of preparing children much better"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 234260.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "for real-life work today."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 238260.0,
      "text": "And indeed, the head of the Chambers of Commerce"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 238260.0,
      "end_time": 241260.0,
      "text": "is now the chairman of the Studio Schools Trust"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 241260.0,
      "end_time": 244260.0,
      "text": "and helping it, not just with big businesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "but small businesses all over the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 249260.0,
      "text": "We started with two schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 251260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s grown this year to about 10."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 251260.0,
      "end_time": 254260.0,
      "text": "And next year, we&#39;re expecting about 35 schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 256260.0,
      "text": "open across England,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 256260.0,
      "end_time": 258260.0,
      "text": "and another 40 areas"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 258260.0,
      "end_time": 260260.0,
      "text": "want to have their own schools opening --"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 260260.0,
      "end_time": 262260.0,
      "text": "a pretty rapid spread"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 264260.0,
      "text": "of this idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 264260.0,
      "end_time": 266260.0,
      "text": "Interestingly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 266260.0,
      "end_time": 269260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s happened almost entirely without media coverage."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 269260.0,
      "end_time": 273260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s happened almost entirely without big money behind it."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 273260.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "It spread almost entirely through word of mouth, virally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 279260.0,
      "text": "across teachers, parents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 279260.0,
      "end_time": 281260.0,
      "text": "people involved in education."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 281260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "And it spread because of the power of an idea --"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 285260.0,
      "text": "so the very, very simple idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 285260.0,
      "end_time": 287260.0,
      "text": "about turning education on its head"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 287260.0,
      "end_time": 290260.0,
      "text": "and putting the things which were marginal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 290260.0,
      "end_time": 293260.0,
      "text": "things like working in teams, doing practical projects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 293260.0,
      "end_time": 296260.0,
      "text": "and putting them right at the heart of learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 296260.0,
      "end_time": 299260.0,
      "text": "rather than on the edges."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 301260.0,
      "text": "Now there&#39;s a whole set of new schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 301260.0,
      "end_time": 303260.0,
      "text": "opening up this autumn."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 303260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "This is one from Yorkshire"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 308260.0,
      "text": "where, in fact, my nephew, I hope, will be able to attend it."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 308260.0,
      "end_time": 310260.0,
      "text": "And this one is focused"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 310260.0,
      "end_time": 312260.0,
      "text": "on creative and media industries."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 312260.0,
      "end_time": 314260.0,
      "text": "Other ones have a focus on health care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 314260.0,
      "end_time": 316260.0,
      "text": "tourism, engineering"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 316260.0,
      "end_time": 318260.0,
      "text": "and other fields."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 318260.0,
      "end_time": 320260.0,
      "text": "We think we&#39;re onto something."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 320260.0,
      "end_time": 322260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not perfect yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 322260.0,
      "end_time": 324260.0,
      "text": "but we think this is one idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 324260.0,
      "end_time": 326260.0,
      "text": "which can transform the lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 326260.0,
      "end_time": 328260.0,
      "text": "of thousands, possibly millions, of teenagers"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 328260.0,
      "end_time": 330260.0,
      "text": "who are really bored by schooling."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 330260.0,
      "end_time": 332260.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t animate them."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 332260.0,
      "end_time": 335260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re not like all of you who can sit in rows"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 335260.0,
      "end_time": 338260.0,
      "text": "and hear things said to you for hour after hour."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 338260.0,
      "end_time": 341260.0,
      "text": "They want to do things, they want to get their hands dirty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 341260.0,
      "end_time": 344260.0,
      "text": "they want education to be for real."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 344260.0,
      "end_time": 346260.0,
      "text": "And my hope is that some of you out there"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 346260.0,
      "end_time": 348260.0,
      "text": "may be able to help us."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 348260.0,
      "end_time": 351260.0,
      "text": "We feel we&#39;re on the beginning of a journey"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 351260.0,
      "end_time": 353260.0,
      "text": "of experiment and improvement"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 353260.0,
      "end_time": 355260.0,
      "text": "to turn the Studio School idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 355260.0,
      "end_time": 358260.0,
      "text": "into something which is present,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 358260.0,
      "end_time": 360260.0,
      "text": "not as a universal answer for every child,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 360260.0,
      "end_time": 363260.0,
      "text": "but at least as an answer for some children in every part of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 363260.0,
      "end_time": 366260.0,
      "text": "And I hope that a few of you at least can help us make that happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 366260.0,
      "end_time": 368260.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 368260.0,
      "end_time": 370260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}